com.biomatters.geneious.publicapi.databaseservice

Class TextOrSimilaritySearchOption

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.biomatters.geneious.publicapi.databaseservice.ExtendedSearchOption
      • com.biomatters.geneious.publicapi.databaseservice.TextOrSimilaritySearchOption

  • public final class TextOrSimilaritySearchOption
extends ExtendedSearchOption
    A specialized option for local search.

    Displayed as an 'Icon-combo-box' with three options: Text Search, Nucleotide Search or Protein Search. Same as the combo-box displayed in the local database search panel.

    The value of this option will be one of TEXT_SEARCH_TYPE, NUCLEOTIDE_SIMILARITY_SEARCH_TYPE or PROTEIN_SIMILARITY_SEARCH_TYPE.

    If this option is attached to the basic search panel, the program will also attempt to automatically select a value in the combo based on what the user has typed, as they type it.
